title: Laura Branigan - Spanish Eddie 320kbps
description:
LAURA BRANIGAN + 1957-2004 +
In memoriam Laura Branigan (3.7.1957 - 26.8.2004), an American singer with exceptional talent and an incredible voice who died too young and abandoned her career way too soon. Feel the power of the 80's. Spanish Eddie is my favorite song of Laura - partly because of the mystery about it but mainly because of the beat. If you don't know Laura Branigan, check her out on YT and TPB. Enjoy+seed.
